title: Leighton Vander Esch going top 10, sneaky WR prospect, Russell Wilson rumors
description:
Pete Prisco joins Will Brinson to break down his latest big board of NFL Draft prospects plus his latest 2018 NFL Mock Draft. The biggest surprise is where he has Leighton Vander Esch (top 10!), but Pete also details his love for a certain quarterback in this class and explains why another surprising quarterback might be the biggest bust of the top group. Prisco has Kolton Miller, not Mike McGlinchey, as his top tackle in the class and names a wide receiver people are sleeping on in the draft class. He also breaks down the Jaguars offseason and reveals a little about their plans in the draft plus a potential fantasy sleeper from the wide receiver corp. Brinson rants about Russell Wilson trade rumors and Pete predicts how many RB will go in the first round.
